Class VersionBoundary

java.lang.Object
  com.i2group.apollo.itemhistoryservice.transport.Boundary
      com.i2group.apollo.itemhistoryservice.transport.VersionBoundary

public final class VersionBoundary
extends Boundary

A Boundary that uses a particular version number to specify one end of a range of Item versions.

A range defined by a VersionBoundary can include a version with the specified number.

2.0
